def rod_cutting(n, prices):
    dp = [0] * (n+1)
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        max_val = float('-inf')
        for j in range(1, i+1):
            max_val = max(max_val, prices[j-1] + dp[i-j])
        dp[i] = max_val
    return dp[n]

n = 8
prices = [1, 5, 8, 9, 10, 17, 17, 20]
print(rod_cutting(n, prices))
